{"TopicId":216930,"ForumId":139,"TopicTitle":"Shine On, You Crazy... Planet?!?","CreatedByName":"Nate Simpson","CreatedById":205123,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-28T21:00:00Z","PageNum":7,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Infinite Aerospace","CreatedById":230192,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-15T16:52:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224330406\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216930\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221697387888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210112\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Scarecrow71\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Scarecrow71 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEven the dev chat videos were delayed after being shot, so they don\u0027t even have time to do those (apparently).\u00A0 Unfortunately, if it walks, looks, and talks like a duck...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eall\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Efor holding out an olive branch, there\u0027s few examples of trust that is so broken it can\u0027t be fixed with mutual engagement. I think we, and the developers alike all share a common interest / passion, the notion of spaceflight and exploration. Kerbal Space Program generally doesn\u0027t appeal to the more common, casual gamer as it\u0027s a bit too involving and \u0027mathy\u0027 to appeal to people who might want a bit of a ruckus shooting people on Call of Duty, not that I\u0027m saying that\u0027s a bad thing at all. Given just how niche the game is, that\u0027s why I think it\u0027s critical to rebuild this discord between the development team and the community. But it takes\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eboth\u003C/strong\u003E parties to do that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-15T17:16:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224330402\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216930\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221697386561\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022230192\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Infinite Aerospace\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n54 minutes ago, Infinite Aerospace said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDakota mentioned over a month ago about some \u0027exciting new stuff\u0027 in 0.1.5 but then has been essentially radio silent about it ever since\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt seems the developers have moved from the \u201Cshow and tell\u201D stage, first to the \u201Ctell\u201D stage, then to the \u201Cevasively tell\u201D stage, and now \u201Cpretend that you are an AAA developer and only communicate with journalists (who really don\u2019t remember about KSP2)\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-15T18:39:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224330402\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216930\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221697386561\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022230192\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Infinite Aerospace\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Infinite Aerospace said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlike is anything actually happening or\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo no, they\u0027re all on Barbados, all year long, taking vacation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-15T20:06:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224330432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216930\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221697395191\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo no, they\u0027re all on Barbados, all year long, taking vacation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nplaying KSP2 on the beach after a difficult hotfix\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Royalswissarmyknife","CreatedById":216092,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-15T20:08:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224330446\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216930\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221697400391\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nplaying KSP2 on the beach after a difficult hotfix\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd then quit after their rocket wobbles itself to destruction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Idealistic","CreatedById":230616,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-20T14:01:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nROOOAAAAARRRRRRR, IM SO HYYYYPPPEEEEE\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}